      "text": "1 ORDER SHEET IN THE HIGH COURT OF SINDH, BENCH AT SUKKUR. Cr.Misc.A. No.S- 484 of 2014. DATE OF HEARING ORDER WITH SIGNATURE OF HON’BLE JUDGE. For Katcha Peshi. 26.06.2014. Mr. Suhail Ahmed Khoso Adv. for applicant. Mr. Zulfiqar Ali Jatoi DPG a/w Akber Ali SHO P:S Sobhodero. Respondent No.3 Mukhtiar present in person. *************** In response to the notice issued on 30.05.2014 by this Court the detainee Mst. Naheed has put up her appearance along with respondent No.3 Mukhtiar. The detainee present in Court has categorically stated that she is wife of the applicant and wants to live with him. She has further stated that respondent No.3 is her brother who has confined her illegally without her wishes. She also stated that she has been beaten by respondent No.3 3⁄4 times in the past. The respondent No.3 present in Court states that applicant is not husband of the detainee and infact she is married to his cousin. The learned DPG present in Court has also stated that in view of the statement of abductee the application be disposed of and the detainee be directed to lead her live with the applicant. Be that as it may, since the detainee present in Court has categorically stated that she is wife of the applicant and has shown her willingness to reside with him, therefore, I do not find any impediment not to allow the detainee to live with the applicant being his legally wedded wife. I have also seen Nikahnama available as annexure-A at page-09 which shows that marriage between the applicant and detainee took placed on 01.06.2007. So far the contentions of respondent No.3 is, he may avail the legal remedy available in the law. 2 Consequently, the application stands disposed of."
